[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps - Classic Pits[/b]
Week 2 of 12 - 2017 Season 1 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]10 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time (qualifying): [b]2:50.197[/b] by Ronny Dudeck
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

Merry Christmas everyone! Week 2 takes us to the historic Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps, affectionately known just as "Spa". This long track makes for epic draft battles with the SRF. Strategy will be key to good results here - time your attacks carefully and plan for a close finish. Let the draft battles commence!

[color=red][b]Three important notes this week: [/b][/color]
[list]As you may already know, Spa is notoriously harsh with off-track penalties. In general the red/white kerbing is [b][color=green]OKAY[/color][/b] while green 'astroturf' outside the track is [b][color=red]NOT OKAY[/color][/b]. To get a 1x the [b]center point of the car[/b] must be over the 'off-track' surface.[/list]
[list]Due to the length of the lap there is only time for ONE qualifying lap. As the offtracks are very tight here it's recommended to be careful to post a valid time![/list]
[list]Due to the Christmas holiday the scheduling of some regular hosted/league/SoF sessions is impacted. Check the details below.[/list]

